    User->>+CLI: datapact validate --contract.yaml --data.csv
    CLI->>+Parser: Parse contract YAML
    Parser->>Parser: Apply policy packs
    Parser-->>-CLI: Contract object
    
    CLI->>+Loader: Load data file
    Loader-->>-CLI: DataFrame
    
